Subject: drm/amdgpu: recover gart table at resume
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 575e55ee4fbc2c641a29b0054b3473e9fa81ae76
